# Ship Checklist

Before every deploy to Vercel:

- `npm run lint` passes
- `npm run build` passes (catches Suspense + type errors)
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` set in Vercel project env vars
- Backend `/health/live` returns 200 (check Render dashboard)
- Smoke test in browser: register → login → see app shell → logout → back to auth
- No secrets in client code (all env vars must be `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` prefixed)
- `useSearchParams` wrapped in `<Suspense>`
- No `console.log` in committed code (use `toast` for user-facing, `console.error` for dev-only)
